{
  "stem": "24171.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You leave the money there, and then when you go later to the latrine, whatever you find there, that's yours.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So there was always-- I was buying more kind of easy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, like an Italian bread, something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was hard to take in too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to make underneath the skirt kind of two loops tied to the-- to the belt and then switch in, kind of, that bread in those loops.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that's how I made a little bit of business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we were not really already that hungry, because if you have a piece of bread, and then you could buy-- I bought once a-- a head of cabbage.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Something green to eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Well, that head-- head of cabbage did me so good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because after that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I mean, we stopped already going there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I worked already in a barrack which we were sorting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The girls were working that time with me to already [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My nieces and my cousin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was the military clothes which came torn or bloody from the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were selecting what could be repaired and what could be thrown out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when we were going-- it was-- that time it was [INAUDIBLE], and actually, we were fasting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came home from the zahlappell, and something was trouble there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their counting was not kind of done the right, proper way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were staying very long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It started to get dark, and we were still in the zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have that cabbage with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- I don't remember if the girls wanted it or didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody was kind of, you know, after a fasting, you know, fasting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You fasted of all the time, but.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
